    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and golden, then transfer to a plate and reserve the pan</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1622200287814-x200.jpg",
