      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves </strong>from their stems, then chop them finely and discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add most<strong> </strong>of the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> mint </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the cooked<strong> </strong>bulgur and give it a good mix – this is your <strong>herby bulgur</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1622200328067-x200.jpg",
